      <body>I fixed this with a different approach, fixing the regex itself. The previous regex was misleading, because since the #{escaped_separator} was inside a zero or one group (ie ()?), it would match trailing zeros after any digit.

I think this is a bit simpler fix, without special casing.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;I fixed this with a different approach, fixing the regex itself.
The previous regex was misleading, because since the
#{escaped_separator} was inside a zero or one group (ie ()?), it
would match trailing zeros after any digit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I think this is a bit simpler fix, without special casing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
